vealed the nature of the stunt.</p>  <figure class=\"element element-image\" data-media-id=\"789e681202a1da2990ffd4c1abd15c1b1e3c740e\"> <img src=\"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2015/3/16/1426498358166/7c0cb1c6-d2b8-4b68-9d22-e9553c2d5227-460x454.jpeg\" alt=\"Ex girlfriend - Ava’s Tinder picture\" width=\"460\" height=\"454\" class=\"gu-image\" /> <figcaption> <span class=\"element-image__caption\">Ex girlfriend - Ava’s Tinder picture</span> </figcaption> </figure>  <p>The picture used on the Tinder profile was of Alicia Vikander, who plays the seductive android in the film. One thwarted amour reported the trick toyed with his emotions “so hard”.</p> <p>While it’s already been released to warm reviews in the UK in January, the film gets US release on 10 April.</p>  <figure class=\"element element-video\" data-canonical-url=\"http://www.theguardian.com/film/video/2015/jan/23/ex-machina-the-gambler-mortdecai-a-most-violent-year-film-show-video-reviews\"                data-short-url=\"http://gu.com/p/4568q\"                        data-show-ads=\"true\"                data-video-id=\"2228795\"                data-video-name=\"The Guardian Film Show: Ex Machina, The Gambler, Mortdecai and A Most Violent Year - video reviews\"                data-video-provider=\"guardian.co.uk\"                data-video-poster=\"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/audio/video/2015/1/23/1422020783206/crop_KP_75619_640x360.jpeg\"> <video data-media-id=\"gu-video-455008638\" class=\"gu-video\" controls=\"controls\" poster=\"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/audio/video/2015/1/23/1422020776567/crop_KP_75619_1200x720.jpeg\"> <source src=\"http://cdn.theguardian.tv/mainwebsite/2015/01/23/150123TheFilmShowSynced_desk.mp4\"></source><source src=\"http://cdn.theguardian.tv/HLS/2015/01/23/150123TheFilmShowSynced.m3u8\"></source><source src=\"http://cdn.theguardian.tv/3gp/large/2015/01/23/150123TheFilmShowSynced_large.3gp\"></source><source