cationDate":"2015-03-16T09:31:36Z","sectionId":"film","id":"film/2015/mar/16/jack-huston-the-crow-remake","fields":{"shortUrl":"http://gu.com/p/46k4c","standfirst":"<p>The actor, known for roles in Boardwalk Empire, American Hustle and the upcoming Ben-Hur remake is to play the comic-book gothic avenger</p>","hasStoryPackage":"false","body":"<p>Jack Huston, the British actor known for Boardwalk Empire, American Hustle and more, has seen his Hollywood cachet grow further with the the news that he’ll take the lead in the upcoming remake of gothic adventure The Crow.</p> <aside class=\"element element-rich-link element--thumbnail\"> <p> <span>Related: </span><a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/culture/2013/dec/01/jack-huston-on-my-radar\">On my radar: Jack Huston's cultural highlights</a> </p> </aside>  <p>The original, based on James O’Barr’s comic book, concerns a man who is brought back to life and sets about avenging the death of his fiancee, guided by a telepathic link with a crow. It topped the box office chart in the US when it was released in 1994, and was made all the more poignant by the death of its lead, Bruce Lee’s son Brandon, who was killed when a gun on set was mistakenly filled with live ammunition.</p> <p>Huston has been rumoured for the role in the remake from director Corin Hardy, but <a href=\"http://www.dreadcentral.com/news/93326/exclusive-jack-huston-confirmed-as-the-crow/\">an interview by Dread Central</a> with O’Barr at a comic convention suggests that it’s a done deal. “Jack Huston has definitely been cast,” O’Barr was reported as saying, and that he was “really happy with that choice.”</p> <p>It’s another eye-catching lead for an actor who has been steadily making his name with acclaimed supporting roles. He gave mobster drama Boardwalk Empire one of its most vivid characters as disfigured war veteran Richard Harrow; played Jack Kerouac in Kill Your Darlings; and rounded out the all-star ensemble in American Hustle. He’s since been cast as Mr Wickham in Austen slash-fic adaptation Pride and Prejudice and Zombies, and in his biggest role yet, <a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/sep/17/jack-huston-morgan-freeman-ben-hur\">he will play Ben-Hur</a> in the remake of the swords-and-sandals epic which is currently filming.</p> <p>It’s a step up for director Hardy too, whose debut feature The Hallow – an Ireland-set horror – was sold at Sundance this year. He previously made music videos for the likes of Keane, Rizzle Kicks, The Prodigy and John Newman.</p>","headline":"Bird man: Jack Huston to take lead in The Crow remake","trailText":"The actor, known for roles in Boardwalk Empire, American Hustle and the upcoming Ben-Hur remake is to play the comic-book gothic avenger","thumbnail":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2015/3/16/1426495666381/a77cbb47-c412-4739-8a0a-2cd14ff006cf-140x84.jpeg","wordcount":"308","commentable":"true","byline":"Ben Beaumont-Thomas","productionOffice":"UK","liveBloggingNow":"false","commentCloseDate":"2015-03-19T09:30:00+00:00"},"webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/mar/16/jack-huston-the-crow-remake","apiUrl":"http://content.guardianapis.com/film/2015/mar/16/jack-huston-the-crow-remake","sectionName":"Film","tags":[{"id":"film/film","webTitle":"Film","type":"keyword","sectionId":"film","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/film/film","apiUrl":"http://content.guardianapis.com/film/film","sectionName":"Film","references":[]},{"id":"film/actionandadventure","webTitle":"Action and adventure","type":"keyword","sectionId":"film","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/film/actionandadventure","apiUrl":"http://content.guardianapis.com/film/actionandadventure","sectionName":"Film","references":[]},{"id":"culture/culture","webTitle":"Culture","type":"keyword","sectionId":"culture","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/culture/culture","apiUrl":"http://content.guardianapis.com/culture/culture","sectionName":"Culture","references":[]},{"id":"books/comic