Herry.</p>","headline":"Elle l’adore review – silly but stylish Chabrol-esque thriller","trailText":"Twists and turns ensue as a middle-aged French pop star gets a devoted fan to help dispose of his girlfriend’s body","thumbnail":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2015/3/11/1426094793759/Elle-Ladore-cranking-up-t-001.jpg","wordcount":"142","commentable":"true","starRating":"3","byline":"Mark Kermode Observer film critic","productionOffice":"UK","liveBloggingNow":"false","commentCloseDate":"2015-04-11T17:24:00+01:00"},"webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/mar/15/elle-ladore-review-silly-stylish-thriller","apiUrl":"http://content.guardianapis.com/film/2015/mar/15/elle-ladore-review-silly-stylish-thriller","sectionName":"Film","tags":[{"id":"film/thriller","webTitle":"Thriller","type":"keyword","sectionId":"film","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/film/thriller","apiUrl":"http://content.guardianapis.com/film/thriller","sectionName":"Film","references":[]},{"id":"film/film","webTitle":"Film","type":"keyword","sectionId":"film","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/film/film","apiUrl":"http://content.guardianapis.com/film/film","sectionName":"Film","references":[]},{"id":"culture/culture","webTitle":"Culture","type":"keyword","sectionId":"culture","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/culture/culture","apiUrl":"http://content.guardianapis.com/culture/culture","sectionName":"Culture","references":[]},{"id":"tone/reviews","webTitle":"Reviews","type":"tone","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/tone/reviews","apiUrl":"http://content.guardianapis.com/tone/reviews","references":[]},{"id":"type/article","webTitle":"Article","type":"type","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/articles","apiUrl":"http://content.guardianapis.com/type/article","references":[]},{"id":"profile/markkermode","webTitle":"Mark Kermode","rcsId":"GNL008099","r2ContributorId":"16060","bylineImageUrl":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2014/4/17/1397749